cs.DL, cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.AI 

The paper discusses the measurement of research performance in universities, which is a topic that falls under several sub-categories in computer science. The use of citation indicators and efficiency indicators is relevant to the sub-categories of digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The analysis of university performance in different fields and disciplines is relevant to the sub-categories of cybernetics (cs.CY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and cryptography (cs.CR).
